# Mission plan

**Execution model:** Squad Leader collects a cosmetic-only bullet list, spawns a **Cosmetic Plan agent** that scaffolds a minimal parent plan and runs **`new-plan`** + **`pr-plan`** inline. **`pr-plan`** spawns **`coding-session`** (Â§5d). Ship execution stays on the detached **`coding-session`** lane; the Squad Leader tracks planning closure and ship progress, then proposes dispatch resolution.

**Skill reuse:** [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/`](.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/) â€” **`new-plan`**, **`pr-plan`**, **`coding-session`**. Spawn contracts: [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/README.md`](.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/README.md).

## Mission constraints (binding)

