|------------|------|
| **Scope** | Cosmetic UI/styling only â€” few lines per item, **no functional behavior changes** |
| **Intake** | Short bullet list; items may be unrelated but all must be cosmetic |
| **PR count** | **Exactly one** PR plan per dispatch (single indexed child) |
| **Skipped** | Full **`author-prd`**, **`planner`** Master Plan, **`pr-breakdown`**, **`delivery-phases`**, **`phase-planner`** |
| **Out of scope redirect** | Functional changes, multi-PR decomposition, or complexity needing Master Plan â†’ **`plan and deliver a single phase`** or **`plan and deliver`** (detached dispatch) |
| **Ship chain** | Same detached **`coding-session`** order as plan-and-deliver Â§8 |

