2. **Single PR plan** â€” Produce one PR plan under `.sedea/operations/` via minimal parent scaffold, **`new-plan`** (indexed child), and **`pr-plan`** inline (Â§Â§1â€“4 populated).

3. **Standard ship** â€” Hand off to **`coding-session`** for implementation and the full plan-and-deliver ship chain (worktree, cut-point, deploy-walk, pre-pr-review, create-pr, pr-review, post-merge cleanup, optional plan-reconcile).

4. **Squad Leader oversight** â€” Track planning completion and detached ship progress; gate **`MC_DISPATCH_RESOLVED_V1`**.

